                                        p We build pretty simple tools and this allows us to take designs simple
                                .col-md-6.col-lg-4
                                    .about-info
                                        i(class="fa fa-eye" aria-hidden="true")
                                        h6 Retina Ready
                                        p We build pretty simple tools and this allows us to take designs simple
                                .col-md-6.col-lg-4
                                    .about-info
                                        i(class="fa fa-headphones" aria-hidden="true")
